One bag contains the following: Skippy Creamy Peanut Butter (28 oz), Bumble Bee Solid White Albacore Tuna in Water (5 oz) X 3, Barilla Classic Blue Box Pasta Elbows (1 lb) OR Barilla Classic Blue Box Pasta Penne (1 lb) OR Barilla Classic Blue Box Pasta Rotini (1 lb), Goya Extra Long Grain Canilla Paraboiled Golden Rice (5 lb) OR Goya Extra Long Grain Canilla Enriched White Rice (5 lb), Market Basket Mixed Vegetables (15 oz) X 3, Hawaiian Punch Fruit Juicy Red Juice Drink (2 L)
